prompts.frontCover: A charming and humorous watercolor greeting card. In the center, a slightly grumpy cartoon capybara is wearing a tiny, tilted blue and white striped party hat. The capybara is relaxing in a Japanese yuzu hot spring, with several bright yellow yuzu fruits floating around it in the steaming water. It has a comically serene, "unimpressed by birthdays" expression. The background is a soft, minimalist wash of pale blue and sage green, suggesting a tranquil spa setting. Floating in the open space above the capybara, the text "Hope your birthday is as relaxing as this." is written in a beautiful, flowing, dark teal handwritten cursive script. The entire illustration is a flat 2D watercolor painting with soft edges, gentle color bleeds, and a lighthearted, clean aesthetic. art by Quentin Blake, Jean-Jacques Sempé. masterpiece, whimsical, high detail.
